  <note line="220" original="pavattā (ka.)" reference-line="107" id="24">
    <extra></extra>
    <alternatives>
      <alternative source-abbr="vri" source="vipassana research institut">kattā</alternative>
      <alternative source-abbr="ka." source="cambodian">pavattā</alternative>
    </alternatives>
    <type>auto</type>
    <snippet>‘Pavivittassāyaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammo, nāyaṃ dhammo saṅgaṇikārāmassā’ti, iti kho panetaṃ vuttaṃ, kiñcetaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ? Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pavivittassa viharato bhavanti upasaṅkamitāro bhikkhū bhikkhuniyo upāsakā upāsikāyo rājāno rājamahāmattā titthiyā titthiyasāvakā. Tatra bhikkhu vivekaninnena cittena vivekapoṇena vivekapabbhārena vivekaṭṭhena nekkhammābhiratena aññadatthu uyyojanikapaṭisaṃyuttaṃyeva kathaṃ kattā </snippet>
  </note>
